:: widgetPosession [widget nobr] {"position":"1000,3100","size":"100,100"}

<<widget "breakFreePossession">>
<<set _maxLevel to _args[0]>>
@@.mc-thoughts; Life and awareness return to you in an instant, and with all the strength you have left, you break free.@@ <br>
<<if $mcpossession lte _maxLevel>>
<<set $mcpossession += 1>>
<b>Surrender to possession</b> is increased: $mcpossession now!<br>
<</if>>
@@.enterbtn; [[Next|possessed]]@@<br>
<</widget>>
